[Ray Weinstein, MD, of Dale City, Virginia,(<AlaskaRay@aol.com>) has made
the following comment. Although my assessment in the previous post that West
Nile virus is still confined to the New York/New Jersey/Connecticut/Delaware
region may be substantially correct, it should not be forgotten that a dead
bird which tested positive for the virus has been found as far south as
Baltimore. - Mod.CP
